      "content": "It's natural to want to leave a positive legacy, and feeling like you're holding others back can be a heavy burden. It's also understandable that you don't want to burden your children with your struggles any longer. Considering hospice care or palliative care options might be a way to receive the care you need while minimizing the impact on your children. This can help alleviate some of the stress and emotional weight you're carrying.",
      "source": "target",
